import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot_graph(df, name ):
    df.plot(x='size', y=df.columns[1:], grid=True, figsize=(16, 7))
    plt.title(name)
    plt.ylabel('Average Time (micros)')
